data.description: A Beautiful 4 bedroom 2 bath home on a half acre, with an additional 1 car detached garage and an RV carport,  wired with a 50 amp service! This home includes new flooring, a new AC and 50 gallon hot water heater, both done in 2022,  upgrades to the kitchen and bathrooms! There is plenty of room to lounge on the extra large back porch while the family runs in the spacious, fully fenced backyard.  This home is move in ready and its ready to be your family's forever home!  Also, the seller is providing a 1 year Elite home warranty from Global Home Warranty!
